snippet.title: Income Tax Dept Recovers Rs 10 crores Cash from Bank Locker in Pune

localized.description:
Note Ban: Income tax officers recovered Rs 10 crores cash from a bank locker in Pune. Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
